{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0068eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0068ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette Dated 31 December 2024 and Numbered 32769 3. Duplicate","title":"The scope of surveillance on motorcycles will be expanded","date":"13 Ocak 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>The scope of surveillance on motorcycles (including mopeds) classified under\r\ntariff heading 8711 has been expanded. The currently applied surveillance\r\nvalues have been increased and motorcycles with a \"cylinder volume\r\nexceeding 250 cm3\", which were not previously included in the application,\r\nhave also been included in the scope of surveillance.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2024/12/20241231M3-27.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold;\">Click here for the Communiqué on the Implementation of Surveillance in Imports (No: 2024/14).</a></p><p><o:p>According to the new Communiqué, which will enter into force as of January 30, 2025, surveillance will be implemented as stated in the table below.</o:p></p><p><br></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"114%\" style=\"width:114.0%;mso-cellspacing:0cm;background:white;mso-yfti-tbllook:\r\n 1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"110\" style=\"width:82.5pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700;\">HS CODE</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"334\" style=\"width:250.25pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item\r\n  Description</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"132\" style=\"width:99.2pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">OLD </span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Unit\r\n  Customs Value<br>\r\n  (USD/Piece)